  "text": "www.mdpi.com/journal/materials Materials 2016, 9, 517 2 of [CITATION_1] Brostow et al. [CITATION_2] proposed a relationship between toughness and brittleness that can be very valuable in relation to expectations for outcomes of material design modifications. Thus, the effect of reinforcement of polymers by a filler or functionalized filler can be evaluated quantitatively.",
